     FANZWP05 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1  10 PGMNM
     I                                       91 170 MSGTXT
     I                                      244 253 WSID
     I                                      254 263 USID
     I                                      264 269 JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@ATK1  1
     C                     PARM           P@ATK2  2
     C                     PARM           P@ATK3  2
     C                     PARM           P@ATK4  1
     C                     PARM           P@UKYY  40
     C                     PARM           P@UKMM  20
     C                     PARM           P@UKDD  20
     C                     PARM           P@UBIN  20
      *
     C                     MOVE P@ATK1    K@ATK1
     C                     MOVE P@ATK2    K@ATK2
     C                     MOVE P@ATK3    K@ATK3
     C                     MOVE P@ATK4    K@ATK4
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKYY    K@UKYY
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKMM    K@UKMM
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKDD    K@UKDD
     C                     Z-ADDP@UBIN    K@UBIN
     C                     MOVE WSID      E@JOBM 10
     C                     MOVE USID      E@USER 10
     C                     MOVE JBNO      E@WNBR  6
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     E@DATE  80
     C           ANZKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@ATK1  1
     C                     KFLD           K@ATK2  2
     C                     KFLD           K@ATK3  2
     C                     KFLD           K@ATK4  1
     C                     KFLD           K@UKYY  40
     C                     KFLD           K@UKMM  20
     C                     KFLD           K@UKDD  20
     C                     KFLD           K@UBIN  20
     C                     KFLD           E@JOBM 10
     C                     KFLD           E@USER 10
     C                     KFLD           E@WNBR  6
